data.description: This charming 2 story in the up and coming Gate District sits on a double corner lot and is just steps from Florist Row. Location is key! Short hop to the City Foundry, the Armory, Busch Stadium and newly opend Top Golf in Midtown. Brand new white oak floors throughout main floor and new carpeting on second floor. Granite tops in kitchen w/ beautiful custom island that leads to back deck, fenced yard and detached 2 car garage. 3 beds and  2 full baths on second floor w/ custom tile floors and showers, spacious second floor laundry is an added bonus.
